---
import { IMG } from '../images';
---

<section class="section bg-forest-950">
  <div class="container-prose grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">The Story</span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-cream-50">
        Built in the shadow of the <span class="italic text-gold-300">Redwoods</span>.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-cream-50/75 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <p>
          Redwood Summit sits inside the Redwood Park development in Rotorua — moments from the Whakarewarewa Forest, one of the world’s great mountain biking destinations and home of Crankworx Rotorua.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're building two properties designed around the rhythm of the ride: wake in the forest, roll out onto 180+ km of trails, return to a spa-warmed recovery lounge and a crew dinner under timbered ceilings.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every detail — from the bike vault to the wash bay to the views from your bed — is there because it earns its place for riders.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src={IMG.forestMorning}
          alt="Morning light through the Whakarewarewa Redwood forest"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
